history.content:
I don't think the 16a waitlist is being processed at the moment as there are enrollment issues. I know this applies to people trying to enroll in the class, but I think it also prevents people from getting off the waitlist. Could be wrong, but I'm pretty sure that's how the calcentral system works (that way someone who has the issue doesn't lose their spot in the class to someone on or off the waitlist).

SO, I would wait to see what happens when this issue is resolved (as there are something like 20 open seats at the moment).
